INSERT INTO `student_info` (`id`, `title`, `feature`, `description`) VALUES
(17, '', 'Guardian Shed', 'Guardian shed is also added as a facility for students. Guardian can stay there for a while in this shed as a guest room which is accommodated about 20 people.'),
(18, '', 'Post Office', 'There is a post office inside the college campus. It has the necessity to post and deliver the important official documents, percels, official letters,personal letters etc. The Post office and post box are active in this college and letters, percels are delivering regularly.'),
(19, '', 'Prayer Room', 'Our Institute has a prayer room. Prayer room is most important of our College. A quiet and large place chosen for prayer room. Every Teachers and stuffs get this facility. Washroom facilities also available for worshipers.'),
(20, '', 'Play Ground', 'Chittagong Mohila Polytechnic institute has a nice architectural view with a playground centered in the middle of the academic building. It is surrounded by the academic and administrative building which is red in color. The annual sports and different types of occasion held in this playground. Students are used to use this playground as a place of passing leisure period.  The Students of architecture department use this playground for their practical task.It has covered with green grass and decorated with different types of flowers.'),
(21, '', 'Canteen', 'Our Institute is providing canteen facility to the students as well as teaching and non teaching staff of the institute; it is capable of catering the demands of the students and can accommodate 40 persons at a time. It has special and properly maintained as well as kitchen, generally the institute provides it to any individual on contract basis after proper official formalities.  The college canteen also caters to the functions organized in the college auditorium and other related programmers like seminars, conferences, and workshops.  Our canteen is nice and clean place.Canteen has tea,Juice,coffee,burger,chocolate,and fresh water.Our Cmpi canteen has healthy food stored. Our canteen is neat and clean. Every Morning students takes tea from canteen. Canteen has special dish for students.'),
(22, '', 'Seminar Hall', 'Seminar room accommodates about 60 to 70 persons. It is fully air-conditioned, suitable for meeting, presentation, and training performance. This room is equipped with projector and large screen which can support documentary film presentation.'),
(23, '', 'Auditorium', 'Chittagong Mohila Polytechnic Institute has spacious auditorium which is perfect for all sports of programe.The auditorium accommodates up to 250 students, teachers and other guests. Other features of the auditorium include: Large stage space, Wi-Fi accessibility, sound and lighting system,2 way doors.'),
(24, '', 'Alternative Power Back Up', 'Government of the People:s Republic of Bangladesh. Chittagong Mohila Polytechnic Institute. An Excellent Place of Technical Education.  Our Institute has a Alternative Power Back It provides quiet, safe, indoor backup power and is a great alternative to a generator. During a power outage, it will automatically supply emergency backup power to household appliances like a refrigerator, TV, light, alarm or sump pump.'),
(25, '', 'Hostel', 'One of the most important facilities which our institute serves to students is hostel facility.Chittagong Mohila Polytechnic Institute was founded in 2005 to create and convey the latest diploma engineering knowledge in ways that would be most useful to the society from which its students came.  The institution is under the management of the Technical Education Board.The Course of studies meets the requirements of the Diploma Engineering conducted by the Technical Education Board. The institute have only four group.'),
(26, '', 'Library', 'Chittagong Mohila Polytechnic Institute,Library Facility There is a beautiful library within institute. Students can collect their necessary books from these libraries. Share her own Choice & Change books we aim to make good use of technology in order to promote our goals and activities. Because it is the Peaceful library our country.  Nowadays CMPI students also collect this library books from Cmpi website Online Library. There is having lots of book collection for every department. Every student can easily download books from Cmpi website online library.'),
(27, '', 'Labs & Workshops', 'Our Institute has Four Department. Each department has separate lab class room. These are electrical Lab, software lab, Networking lab, Hardware lab, Architecture lab, Garments machine lab etc and also have Physics lab, Chemistry Lab.  Every department has a separate lab and workshops. Every lab class and workshop has one Lab Assistant .He manages this lab class room. Lab Assistant maintain lab instrument and help students for basic Knowledge in lab works. Lab Assistant follow lab Class Schedule and help students increase their technical skills.'),
(28, '', 'Multimedia Class Room', 'Our Institute arranged multimedia class room for every department students.Basically Computer Students benefits this multimedia class room. Every lab class room has Projector for make teaching and training more effective and enjoyable for both students & teachers.  Establishing Multimedia Classrooms in secondary schools, training teachers on making ICT aided educational content on hard-to-grasp topics and make electronic versions of text books available in primary and secondary levels including technical, vocational and Madrasa institutions. Multimedia class room is necessary and most important in our Educational area.  So our Institute every teacher practical class takes by projector, so students easily catches their instruction.  The education initiatives by access to information project aim to make teaching and learning more effective and enjoyable for both students and teachers using ICT. Establishing Multimedia classroom in this institution learning a new revolution in polytechnic sector. Teachers of this institution are well trained to make multimedia based lecture sheet and content. Because with the help of ICT based learning government wants to turn the large pool of intelligent young citizens into valuable human resources the needs of 21 century.Refeshioning classroom environment and redesigning the tools of learning, teachers want to envisioned education reform');

